cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the hardware log level to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause logging configuration errors and potential system instability.
du.explanation_zh: 將硬體日誌級別設定為無效值 'invalid' 會導致日誌配置錯誤，並可能造成系統不穩定。
